the training\nlatency by $99\\%$ over the prior FHE-based technique on various encrypted\ndatasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Nov 2019 21:30:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 19:22:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 22 Oct 2020 02:09:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-23"}
