ises the underlying quadratic\ninteractions in the SSP of the minimal channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Nov 2019 23:44:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 17:28:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 Nov 2020 21:16:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
