achine translation tasks. In addition, MUSE has potential\nfor accelerating inference due to its parallelism. Code will be available at\nhttps://github.com/lancopku/MUSE\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Nov 2019 09:36:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-22"}
